Package Automata.TwoDimentions.GoL

Class GameOfLife

  • java.lang.Object
    • Automata.Automaton
      • Automata.TwoDimentions.Automaton2Dim
        • Automata.TwoDimentions.GoL.GameOfLife
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    GameOfLifeGriddy, GameOfLifeNonGriddy

    public abstract class GameOfLife
extends Automaton2Dim

The base class for every game of life automaton. The "mode" field of the base class "Automaton" stores the amounts of
neighbors alive that can make a dead cell alive and keep a cell alive alive.
